---
const svgTarget = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-rose-400"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>`;
const svgMapPin = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-blue-400"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>`;
const svgLightbulb = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-amber-400"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.9 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"/><path d="M9 18h6"/><path d="M10 22h4"/></svg>`;
const svgGlobe = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-emerald-400"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>`;
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="relative py-32 px-6 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16">
      <!-- Left text -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-300 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-6 reveal delay-100">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
          Sobre Mí
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 reveal delay-200">
          Construyo cosas con <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-500">propósito</span>.
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed reveal delay-300 mb-10">
          <p>
            Soy un desarrollador apasionado por crear experiencias digitales que
            combinan funcionalidad con estética. Llevo más de 3 años trabajando
            en proyectos web, siempre buscando la intersección entre código
            limpio y diseño cuidadoso.
          </p>
          <p>
            Me especializo en el stack moderno de JavaScript/TypeScript, con
            enfoque en rendimiento, accesibilidad y experiencia de usuario. Cada
            proyecto es una oportunidad para aprender algo nuevo y dejar una
            huella.
          </p>
          <p>
            Fuera del código, me encuentras explorando diseño, escuchando música
            o aprendiendo algo que no tiene nada que ver con tecnología.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 reveal delay-400">
          <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0 1 12 6.844a9.59 9.59 0 0 1 2.504.337c1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.02 10.02 0 0 0 22 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"/>
            </svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 0 1-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 1 1 2.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="/cv.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 text-emerald-400 font-medium hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-all">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/>
            </svg>
            Descargar CV
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right cards -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4">
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors reveal delay-200">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-rose-500/10 border border-rose-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <Fragment set:html={svgTarget} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Enfoque</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Full-Stack Development</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors reveal delay-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <Fragment set:html={svgMapPin} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Ubicación</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Chile — Remoto global</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors reveal delay-400">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <Fragment set:html={svgLightbulb} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Intereses</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-white">UX Design, OSS, AI Tools</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors reveal delay-500">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <Fragment set:html={svgGlobe} />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Idiomas</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Español · Inglés</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20 reveal delay-500 mt-2">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(16,185,129,0.8)] animate-pulse shrink-0"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-emerald-400 font-semibold">Disponible para proyectos</div>
            <div class="text-emerald-500/60 text-sm font-medium mt-1">Freelance · Full-time · Consultoría</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
